Mybuild
=======

Collection of ocamlbuild plugins


How to use
==========

Call `ocamlbuild -use-ocamlfind -plugin-tags package\(mybuild\)` (backslash escapes parentheses from shell).

For OASIS-enabled projects, add

  override BUILDFLAGS = "-use-ocamlfind -plugin-tags package\(mybuild\)"

on top of generated Makefile (before `OASIS_START` section).

Every plugin is in separate `Mybuild` submodule. Plugins should be enabled explicitely in `myocamlbuild.ml`, e.g.:

  open Mybuild
  let () =
    Version.save "version.ml";
    OCaml.setup ();
    Extprot.setup ()
